    "Pocket Scanner syncs your documents across devices through iCloud Drive. You can use the app without it — scans will stay on this device only." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the benefits of using iCloud Drive with Pocket Scanner.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pocket Scanner sincroniza tus documentos entre dispositivos a través de iCloud Drive. Puedes usar la app sin él: los escaneos se quedarán solo en este dispositivo."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pocket Scanner synchronise vos documents entre vos appareils via iCloud Drive. Vous pouvez utiliser l'app sans cela — les numérisations resteront uniquement sur cet appareil."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pocket Scanner uses your camera to capture documents. Enable access in Settings." : {
